{"title":"海南人歌（二首）","authors":["晨声"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南人歌（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岛宴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！别客气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您的第二故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烹调　海味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一席丰盛的五指山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舀一碗站起来的风浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举满杯热辣辣的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敞怀共饮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个痛痛快快的海南……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个浪都是一座山峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臂臂相挽环筑千百道抗风的墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次被推倒，摔碎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次将信念举向天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每棵林木都长着蓬勃的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根巴着根脉络扎进思考的深层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南人的头发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦树起，也能撕碎台风……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：广州市诗歌业余作者）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}